pkgc:ID_153605888 a skos:Concept ;
    dc:date "2020-05-01"^^xsd:date ;
    skos:prefLabel "We are looking for a data-minded Product Manager to join the Personalization Platform team. The Personalization Platform team builds models, tools, and data products to represent personalization, discovery, content relationships, and the APIs to serve those models. These products enable Data Scientists and Machine Learning teams to understand foundational aspects of user journeys and the listening life cycle in order to build compelling, personalized features. You will work with highly skilled engineers to iterate on the data products and evolve the platform, and communicate with stakeholders and clients around vision and roadmaps. Your work will power models and data-driven decision making across the organization that directly influence personalized experiences for users." ;
    pkg:sourceMap "careerDevelopment.mm" .

