pkgc:ID_358735911 a skos:Concept ;
    dc:date "2025-09-17"^^xsd:date ;
    skos:prefLabel "Director, Technical Product Management 1. You will be the Product leader with the highest level of technical expertise in the team. While you will have a team of Product Managers, you are expected to be hands-on and truly be part of the delivery process. Are you comfortable with being more tactical than strategic? 2. Are you willing to create technical user stories/epics to build from scratch a public (client facing) API which will allow clients to accept payments such as credit/debit card, wallets (google pay, PayPal), ACH and instant payment methods? 3. Can you create requirements for Dev teams to build from scratch cross border and local settlement engines? 4. Have you implemented tokenization and fraud monitoring solutions?" ;
