pkgc:ID_487768538 a skos:Concept ;
    dc:date "2025-03-07"^^xsd:date ;
    skos:prefLabel """Over the last 18 months I've become convinced that we're at the precipice of a complete transformation in the world of work, driven by structured data, LLMs and AI agents. Using Claude, Grok and more recently, Deepseek daily has supercharged my productivity, and made projects which were stuck in my backlog for years, suddenly levels of magnitude easier to implement.

However, due to security and privacy concerns, and a lack of understanding of high impact use cases and tooling, most users in the enterprise today do not benefit from similar gains in their daily productivity at work.

Working at anthropic will combine my extensive enterprise experience with a passion for improving business processes with information systems and finding ways to use this to drive value for our clients.""" ;
    pkg:sourceMap "careerDevelopment.mm" .

